research_municipality_step.notes: The information for elected officials was gathered from the City of Meadowlakes website and a news article regarding the May 2024 elections. There was a discrepancy for Council Member Place 1, where the city website listed Mike Shaw, but a news article from May 7, 2024, indicated Don Wheeler won the election for Place 1 and would be sworn in on May 21, 2024. The news article's results were prioritized for the most current information. Carolyn Richmond was confirmed as Council Member Place 3 and Mayor Pro-Tem.

office.name: Council Member - Mayor Pro Tempore - Place 3
